Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:39.92,biaoti2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,285)}幽靈村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長  請進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香大小姐也請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永谷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  這次也沒有目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是在乘客稀少的時間段嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹啥  室戶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是來推銷新書的話  直接送到署裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我是不會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  今天不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對這次事件我有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是殺人事件  不是室戶先生喜歡的怪談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又給我來這套  我可是聽到一些傳聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你是說那個無聊的傳聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是說聽到歌聲那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是詛咒之歌  死亡之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來自靈界的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在網上可是炒得沸沸揚揚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人事件發生的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從收音機和電視裡傳來女孩子的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個花子啊  半截怪啊啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過去好像蠻有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲被錄下來流傳到網上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,北村啊  你信這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  你們不信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為報道研究會的人  應該會感興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在畢業的前輩裡  不是有很擅長這方面的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不算  室戶學長是報道研之恥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我憧憬的是真田香里學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我對這種怪論沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪論！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  即然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪談？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的星球上也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷納比亞的遙控人偶裡有庫帕幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還下載了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼讓人不舒服的歌沒必要特地放給我們聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別放啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喔…中杉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  中杉  這邊  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說我嗎？  你從哪進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  你是住在附近的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不能隨便就進別人家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著擔心  姐姐你有守護天使保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}下一則新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}連續幾天  以地鐵丸之內線為中心發生的連續殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}至今未能發現有力的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}搜查陷入困境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個吧  今天在學校談論的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}根據法醫生的解剖鑒定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}迄今為止死亡的四人死因都是胸部受到重壓導致內臟破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛  那麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛穿上寫真偶像的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別在意這些小事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點在意那個事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  總覺得在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個詛咒之歌的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被害人的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據我今天聽到的情報  像是被大猩猩什麼的勒死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我覺得再深入調查一下會很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  取材費能再多撥點給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我一定出色地搞到您要的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  這下就能堅持一段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊只能先放一放了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是有田紫苑呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到老奸巨猾的交到個女朋友和有田紫苑一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那個  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  趕緊找個理由閃人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去調查事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我差不多該告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣  正在興頭上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  喝吧  喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我喝完就走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  海量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是什麼惡劣的惡作劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是昨天不是出現了受害者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,時間正好是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是犯人的伎倆？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干擾電波  播放歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真要和事件有關的話  新聞什麼的應該會說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種傳聞  警察會重視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天要不是你姐姐來搗亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己玩得那麼起勁還敢說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧發生事件  可以確定大致範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,專家辦事就是不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過與我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底是你私自開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家的媒體很容易操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了  您認識受害者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼室戶前輩會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經無路可逃了  有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這不是室戶前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…你是早宮的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一川  不對  萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  有田紫苑進到這裡來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一看就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}下一站  新宿  新宿  出口在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的也是？難道又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽到歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊  巴迪覺得那個事件和硫加有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能確定  但我覺得有牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是硫加會殺人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是危險品了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想對地球人來說肯定也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  可疑的地方都拿出來好好調查一番
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的黑網站  有點讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人給人的印象是不是差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者都是短髮帶眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了  小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室戶  你在這做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  我想著這身打扮犯人就會出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長  請等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木君  到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會…會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太激動對身體不好哦  中杉會長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生  你說出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,膽小的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏瑪朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,社會上炒得沸沸揚揚的連續殺人事件的犯人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡逃走的傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也聽說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡開發的傀儡木偶並不是單純的看護用機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒聽說是用於戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的以為是在製造看護用機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我給這研究所投了多少錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母親！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是與永谷主任擁有相同特徵的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是她設定的程式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,設定了對自己撒嬌的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,M程式的解析已經成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  但是出現了BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還陪著你做白日夢是無法在世上生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的人都清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了使傀儡木偶能夠自主行動而開發的M程式是黑匣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在被打開了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某國的軍方研究室都沒成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這證明了你的部下很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你從哪搞到傀儡木偶的基礎設計方案的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這你不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊  我教你的歌記住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子  記住了媽媽的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  是媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼晚才給你調整眼睛  對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽最喜歡你了  來抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜歡媽媽了  來抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,調查下這傢伙的話  能找到點線索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  那就帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,監護者？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是聯邦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘  馬上就要下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛接到部下報告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶的電波突然中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看情況要順利捕捉到它很困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  剛才的聲音是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到傀儡木偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩木偶遊戲可以  但善後要做好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然你尋找的寶物就要被人橫刀奪愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,守護天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能交個朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是有田紫苑呐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都好熱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種酷暑去山中避暑真是不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  功君他們好像要去中杉小姐家的別墅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君內心一目了然  激動不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這愉快的氣氛被不得了的事件給浮雲了  哇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,==================================
